522
01:00:47,886 --> 01:00:49,388
Maka kita akan berjumpa lagi.

523
01:00:50,097 --> 01:00:51,515
Segera.

524
01:00:52,266 --> 01:00:53,558
Selamat tinggal, Philip.

525
01:00:53,684 --> 01:00:55,853
