01:07:11,820 --> 01:07:13,030
Tunggu!

607
01:07:15,324 --> 01:07:16,700
Tuan putri?

608
01:07:24,792 --> 01:07:26,252
Aku mencari seorang gadis.

609
01:07:26,544 --> 01:07:28,129
Tentu saja.

610
01:07:32,842 --> 01:07:34,469
Aku butuh seekor kuda.

611
01:07:51,111 --> 01:07:56,366
