Raja John dari Ulstead.

652
01:13:20,906 --> 01:13:22,616
Seorang pangeran!

653
01:13:33,753 --> 01:13:35,254
Aurora.

654
01:13:36,339 --> 01:13:38,216
Dia mengenal Aurora.

655
01:13:39,759 --> 01:13:41,093
Kenapa dia tidur?

656
01:13:41,219 --> 01:13:43,805
Dia dalam kuasa sebuah mantra.

657
01:13:43,888 --> 01:13:46,349
Dia cantik, bukan?

658
01:13:47,392 --> 01:13:49,936
Gadis tercantik
yang pernah kulihat.

659
01:13:51,229 --> 01:13:53,314
Kau mau menciumnya?

660
01:13:54,899 --> 01:13:56,025
